</br>
Type of articles - technical descriptive articles.
</br>
1. R&D and behavioral psychology and predictive analytics in car babysitting and child taxi ordering services - to talk about the experience of creating a technological check and preventing crimes against children''s integrity in the service;
</br>
2. How is the system for checking drivers in the services of ordering car nannies and children''s taxi kids.taxi.
</br>
</br>
The writer is provided with:
</br>
1. Access to all developers: all our developers are ready to tell you about the processes in as much detail as possible, there will be no problems with this.
</br>
2. Flowcharts, snippets with code, etc. can be used in the text.
</br>
</br>
Audience: developers, heads of technical departments, directors of technology startups with technical education.', 0, N'', 0, N'', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, N'', 1, CAST(N'2022-08-27T05:00:00.0000000' AS DateTime2), 0, 1)
